criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  STEMI patients undergoing coronary angiography and PCI;

          -  can complete 3 follow-up visits well.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  without PCI;

          -  undergoing thrombolytic therapy;

          -  mental diseases;

          -  renal failure;

          -  stroke sequelae;

          -  tumor and a history of revascularization.
